	<documentation>
Axxess Vestibule Station

Three Button Vestibule Station

Features:
	Button 1:	Do Not Disturb
	Button 2:	Housekeeping
	Button 3:	Master Lights

-----------------
Properties
-----------------

Debug Mode:
	Used for debugging the driver. Output is displayed on the Lua tab.
	Options:
		Off
		Print
		Log
		Print and Log

-----------------
Events
-----------------
	C4 Keypad Proxy Events (Button 1 2 3):
	* Button Press
	* Button Release
	* Button Single Tap
	* Button Double Tap
	* Button Triple Tap

	Device Specific Events:
	* Do Not Disturb On
	* Do Not Disturb Off
	* Housekeeping On
	* Housekeeping Off
	* Master Control
	* Doorbell Ring
	* Master On
	* Master Off
	* Do Not Disturb Toggled
	* Housekeeping Toggled

-----------------
Commands
-----------------
	Device Specific Commands:
	* Do Not Disturb
	  - On/Off
	* Housekeeping
	  - On/Off
	* Master
	  - On/Off
	* Doorbell
	  - On/Off
	* Doorbell Ring

-----------------
Connections
-----------------
	The following connections are available:
	* ZIGBEE

----------------- End Documentation --------------------
